118
00:07:35,663 --> 00:07:37,978
Donc, déterminons

119
00:07:40,301 --> 00:07:43,681
si <i>T</i> est bijective.

120
00:07:44,598 --> 00:07:48,580
Je vais faire, comme d'habitude,
la chose la plus simple.

121
00:07:48,580 --> 00:07:50,223
