129
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:20,058
J'ai <i>a₁ - a₂ = 0</i>,

130
00:08:21,348 --> 00:08:24,101
<i>a₂ - a₃ = 0 </i>,

131
00:08:24,981 --> 00:08:28,589
<i> a₃ - a₀ = 0</i>,

132
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:31,252
