j'obtiens que <i>a₂ = 0</i>.

138
00:08:48,628 --> 00:08:50,796
Et ensuite que <i>a₁ = 0</i>.

139
00:08:52,286 --> 00:08:54,433
Ça, si on remonte, c'est très facile.

140
00:08:54,983 --> 00:08:56,119
Du coup, le noyau

141
00:08:57,899 --> 00:08:58,709
de <i>T</i>,

142
00:08:59,129 --> 00:09:00,129
c'est juste,

143
00:09:01,129 --> 00:09:03,823
(ici, j'ai <i>a₀ = 0</i> aussi)

144
00:09:03,823 --> 00:09:05,629
donc c'est juste le polynôme <i>0</i>.

145
00:09:06,179 --> 00:09:09,110
Et donc, <i>T</i> est injective.

146
00:09:10,850 --> 00:09:12,273
Donc, par le corollaire,

147
00:09:13,496 --> 00:09:15,866
